# Privacy Policy for MemoK

**Last Updated: January 12, 2026**

## Overview

MemoK ("we," "our," or "the app") is a voice recording application designed with privacy as a core principle. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information.

## Data Collection

**We do not collect any personal data.**

MemoK operates entirely offline and locally on your device. We do not:
- Collect personal information
- Track your location
- Access your contacts
- Monitor your usage behavior
- Use analytics or tracking tools
- Display advertisements

## Audio Recordings

All audio recordings created by MemoK are:
- **Stored locally** on your device only
- **Never uploaded** to any external server
- **Never shared** with third parties
- **Fully under your control** - you can delete them at any time

## Data Storage

- All recordings are saved in your device's local storage
- Starred recordings are protected from automatic cleanup
- You can export or share recordings manually through your own actions
- Uninstalling the app will remove all recordings from your device

## Third-Party Services

MemoK does not integrate with any third-party services, analytics platforms, or advertising networks.

## Children's Privacy

MemoK does not knowingly collect any information from children under 13 years of age.

## Legal Compliance

Users are responsible for complying with local laws regarding audio recording and consent. Please ensure you have appropriate permissions before recording conversations.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us by opening an issue at:

**https://github.com/RichradsY/MemoKapp**

---

*MemoK - Your recordings stay with you.*
